cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques, specifically the computation and visualization of image gradients. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves some artistic transformations of images, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of machine learning for style transfer could also place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
